rows.label: tlk70000021_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Maquia's personality has mellowed
out a bit lately. She used to be
out of control. A total bad egg.

rows.label: tlk70000021_04_msg0002
rows.name:
She stole and manipulated people on a
daily basis. Believe me - I was one of
her victims, so you know it's true.

rows.label: tlk70000021_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Of course, the one who really bore the
brunt of it was my master, though I've
only come to realize that recently.

rows.label: tlk70000021_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I think maybe she just didn't know
any other way to behave around people.
She must've had a rough life.

rows.label: tlk70000021_04_msg0005
rows.name:
You think you know someone, but
you've really just scratched the
surface... People sure are confusing.
